Title: Bambu Lab PETG-HF (red vs blue) as a replacement for PETG Basic, but is it really better?. Watch on youtube: https://youtu.be/gWMSbIRMRJc Tags: 3dprint , material test , bambulab , petg , Bambu Lab PETG HF is a High Flow version of PETG Basic filament, which will be discontinued. This new filament can be printed on a two times bigger flow rate, but how does it affect the mechanical properties? Let's find out.
